This paper discusses the use of Information Centric Networking (ICN) technology for federating NoSQL databases, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of real data sets, which suggests a focus on networking and communication (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper discusses performance evaluation, which could fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
